  "status": "active",
  "version": 1,
  "summary": "End Matter ISI/legal footer uses locked scale: ISI subheads 14px Bold, 'IMPORTANT RISK INFORMATION' 15px Bold, ISI body 13px Regular (1.4 lh), footnotes/legal 11px Regular; not styled by editorial defaults."
